    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "function lengthOfLongestSubstring(s) {\n  const seen = new Set();\n  let left = 0, best = 0;\n  for (let right = 0; right < s.length; right++) {\n    while (seen.has(s[right])) {\n      seen.delete(s[left]);\n      left++;\n    }\n    seen.add(s[right]);\n    best = Math.max(best, right - left + 1);\n  }\n  return best;\n}\n\nconsole.log(lengthOfLongestSubstring(\"abcabcbb\")); // 3 (\"abc\")"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Сложность: O(n) по времени, O(алфавит) по памяти." }]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": { "level": 3 },
      "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "3) Минимальная подстрока, содержащая все символы T (Min Window Substring)" }]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Поддерживаем частоты требуемых символов. Расширяем окно до выполнения условия, затем сужаем, минимизируя длину." }]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "function minWindow(s, t) {\n  if (t.length === 0) return \"\";\n  const need = new Map();\n  for (const ch of t) need.set(ch, (need.get(ch) || 0) + 1);\n\n  let have = 0, required = need.size;\n  const window = new Map();\n  let left = 0, ans = [-1, 0, 0]; // [len, l, r]\n\n  for (let right = 0; right < s.length; right++) {\n    const c = s[right];\n    window.set(c, (window.get(c) || 0) + 1);\n    if (need.has(c) && window.get(c) === need.get(c)) have++;\n\n    while (have === required) {\n      if (ans[0] === -1 || right - left + 1 < ans[0]) ans = [right - left + 1, left, right];\n      const cl = s[left];\n      window.set(cl, window.get(cl) - 1);\n      if (need.has(cl) && window.get(cl) < need.get(cl)) have--;\n      left++;\n    }\n  }\n\n  return ans[0] === -1 ? \"\" : s.slice(ans[1], ans[2] + 1);\n}\n\nconsole.log(minWindow(\"ADOBECODEBANC\", \"ABC\")); // \"BANC\""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Сложность: O(n) по времени, O(алфавит) по памяти." }]
